oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Drug Inventory Control
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Porter, Bonnie Sue
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Is there anyone here that has an inventory control monitoring system of some kind in their practice? Two? Tell me something. What do you tell the client that tells you "I don't need to write that down, I can keep it in my head, I remember every bit of it." Keeping track of inventory can make one or many differences in your practice
